          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Show that you know first aid for, and the prevention of, injuries or illnesses that could occur while welding, including electrical shock, eye injuries, burns, fume inhalation, dizziness, skin irritation, and exposure to hazardous chemicals, including filler metals and welding gases."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
